│ entire isKnownInversion function)\n\nThe function should be updated to      │
│ include a check that both icmp instructions either have samesign or both    │
│ don't have samesign.\n\n5. Conclusion:\n\nBy adding a check for matching    │
│ samesign attributes in `isKnownInversion`, we prevent the incorrect         │
│ transformation of select instructions where the two icmp operands have      │
